    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>

                <p>Your kind Letter reached me here safely. I thank <persName ref="pe0192">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Elliot</persName> for his kind present which I
                    suppose (owing to the times is not yet arrived. I have got one of <persName ref="pe0156">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Lows</persName> best <rs ref="ar0204">drawings</rs> new done
                    by a skilful hand &amp; given it to an engraver &amp; will send him proofs as
                    soon as finished. I hope in time to get him information about the brass things.
                    If he goes over the same ground, he must incorporate his new information with
                    the old. I sent his <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0422">nat.
                        history</title></bibl> to <persName ref="pe0043">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                            Cadel</persName>; &amp; hope <persName ref="pe0104">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        Gough</persName> has taken like care of the <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0058">journal</title></bibl>. If you write again, to me here it must be
                    by return of post, for I quit town very soon. I had only a glimpse of <persName ref="pe0104">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Gough</persName>, for by unlucky
                    coincidence of engagements we cannot see each other.</p>
                <closer><salute>I remain D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Sir <lb/>faithfully y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Tho. Pennant</persName></signed>

                <dateline><placeName ref="pl0699">London</placeName> April 24<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> 1778.</dateline></closer>


                <postscript>
                    <p>I hope you got my <bibl type="authorial"><title ref="bi0012">Welsh
                            Tour</title></bibl>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> G. Paton</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>Custom house</addrLine>
                    </address></p>
            </div>
